-- NDRC Sees No Foundation to Cut China Residential Power Price, Xinhua Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-13T00:12:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/ndrc-sees-no-foundation-to-cut-china-residential-power-price-xinhua-says.html
China’s National Development and
Reform Commission sees no foundation to support a cut of China’s
overall residential power price at the moment, the official
Xinhua News Agency reported, citing Cao Changqing, director of
commodity pricing at the country’s top economic planner.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
